title: 이달의소녀탐구 #76 (LOONA TV #76)
summary:
The girls are sleepy as they arrive at their destination.
0:03 -- YeoJin: “Hello~. Where are we?”. HyunJin: “Taiwan~”. HaSeul: ”Yes, yes~”
0:14 -- HyunJin mentions that this is the last day of shooting. She takes over as the PD
and shows that HeeJin is having a photoshoot with a cat.
0:24 -- HeeJin: “December 25th, 2016. Christmas in Taiwan!”
The girls are working hard even though it is Christmas.
